{"tid":507474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=??  71歲替更清潔工冬至開工　墮垃圾槽困2小時亡","createTime":"2017-12-23T09:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T12:48:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd18517b2540d88a9a200a4f873e6b410fdee52","tid":507474,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T09:50:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回歸垃圾的懷抱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山發生工人墮垃圾槽死亡意外。昨晚(22日)10時許，警方接獲報案，指錦泰苑錦邦閣有清潔男工在30樓傾倒垃圾期間，懷疑失足跌進約半米乘半米的垃圾槽，<span style=\"color: red;\">頭下腳上「倒豎蔥」卡在29至30樓垃圾槽之間</span>，警方及消防接報趕至，消防處派出高空拯救專隊及攀山拯救專隊救援，威爾斯親王醫院亦派醫生到場。至今日凌晨零時許，消防將被困工人救出，他已經昏迷，由救護車送院搶救後不治。警方初步調查事件無可疑，列作工業意外處理，死因有待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n喪生工人71歲姓羅，有認識該工人的街坊表示，他在錦邦閣做清潔工多時，早上6時已見其掃垃圾，晚上又見他在地下垃圾房工作，他曾表示因兼職才做「咁長時間」。約10日前，由於在錦邦閣倒垃圾的女工辭職，工友需輪流到錦邦閣倒垃圾，昨晚冬至輪到事主，結果發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171223/bkn-20171223005746159-1223_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b06052fb73016080efadea5552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171223%2Fbkn-20171223005746159-1223_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D402882b06052fb73016080efadea5552&d=YNG%2ByCLZrigdDwYgCyUwpgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=4122c17e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171223/bkn-20171223005746159-1223_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b06052fb73016080efadea5552</a>"},{"pid":"460a4444f1cdc2ca134fa8cd51eccde1ee0bcb10","tid":507474,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":96,"score":-95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"頭下腳上「倒豎蔥」卡在29至30樓垃圾槽之間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /